description:
Doors open at 6p.m.

The first talk, by Jorge Silva, “Bitcoin and Cryptocurrencies - From Zero to Hero”, will begin at 6.30p.m.
Around 7p.m., Vânia Gonçalves takes over the stage and tells us about “G2PT: Women in Technology”.

There’ll be a coffee break, make sure to say hello.

Dedicated WiFi: MoB Session.
Entrance is free.

For more info, go to www.makeorbreak.io/#sessions
name: MoB Session at Blip
